</item>
<item>
<title><code>func</code></title>
  <p>returns true to continue check for
                                      the location and false to filter the location out</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>the city closest to (<code>lat</code>, <code>lon</code>), in the
         region or administrative district of <code>loc</code> with validation of filter function.</p>
